import React from "react"
import { HashRouter, Route } from "react-router-dom"
import Homepage from "./Component/Homepage"
import Secondpage from "./Component/Secondpage"
import Reacthooksdemo from "./Component/Reacthooksdemo"
import Student from "./Component/Student"
import Api from "./Component/Api"
import MainPage from "./Resume-Builder/MainPage"
import Acount from "./Resume-Builder/Acount"
import About from "./Resume-Builder/About"
import Test from "./Resume-Builder/Test"
import Blog from "./Resume-Builder/NewsApi"

const Routes = () => {

    return (
        <HashRouter>
            {/* <Route exact path="/" component={Homepage} />
            <Route exact path="/Secondpage" component={Secondpage} />
            <Route exact path="/Reacthooksdemo" component={Reacthooksdemo} />
            <Route exact path="/Student" component={Student} />
            <Route exact path="/Api" component={Api} /> */}
            <Route exact path="/" component={MainPage} />
            <Route exact path="/Acount" component={Acount} />
            <Route exact path="/About" component={About} />
            <Route exact path="/NewsApi" component={Blog} />
            <Route exact path='/test' component={Test} />
          </HashRouter>
    )
}

export default Routes
